meta {
  name: StartSession
  type: http
  seq: 1
}

post {
  url: {{base_url}}/Cortina/StartSession
  body: json
  auth: none
}

body:json {
  {
    "TokenId": "token-123",
    "RandomNumber": "123456789012345678901234567",
    "DynamicURL": "https://your-server.example.com/alt",
    "CustomData": {
      "Actor": "12312312",
      "Distributor": "superDistributor"
    }
  }
}

docs {
  Direction: Nayax → Integrator. Nayax calls this on your server to start a session.

  The integrator must:
  1. Generate a 36-digit Transaction ID
  2. Encrypt it using the last 32 chars of the Secret Token as AES-256 ECB key
  3. Return the encrypted TranIDCipher

  Auth: AES-256 ECB encryption with PKCS5 padding. Key = last 32 chars of Secret Token.
}
